## Write a program to convert miles to feet

1 mile = 5280 feet

```txt
Input  : 5
Output : 26400
```

---

<CodeBlock slug="convert-miles-to-feet" >

```c
#include <stdio.h>

int main()
{
    int miles;
    scanf("%d", &miles);
    int feet = miles * 5280;
    printf("%d", feet);
}
```

